# Old WordPress glossary + category archives (20/07/2026).
# These were still returning hard 404s while pulling impressions in Search Console
# (/glossary/display-advertising/ alone did 922 in 90 days). The content is gone and
# not worth reviving (it drew international definition-seekers, not NZ buyers), so
# these splats just park the remaining link equity on /insights.
# Splats live at the END of the file: Wrangler warns that any exact rule sitting
# below a splat is matched less efficiently.
/glossary                  /insights          301
/glossary/                 /insights          301
/category                  /insights          301
/category/                 /insights          301
/glossary/*                /insights          301
/category/*                /insights          301
